Deathchase is one of those &quot;good in its time&quot; games. Return of the Jedi was fresh in everybody's minds, and this emulated one of the best scenes in it. It's horribly basic, but I liked it back in '84 or '85. But it's so one-dimensional that it definitely isn't the &quot;best game ever&quot;, and even in 1986/7 it was showing its age. YS kept giving its rerelease 6/10 or so.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=73">Chuckie</a> — Tue Jul 12, 2011 2:43 pm</p><hr />
